====Usage notes====
As a transitive verb, this can take the usual {{l|en|accusative}} {{l|en|particle}} {{ja-r|を}} after the object of the verb.  However, it is much more common to see this with the {{l|en|quotative}} particle {{ja-r|と}} instead.

